title: ICommandTab.IGetCommandTabBoxes
description: Gets the CommandManager tab boxes on this CommandManager tab.

parameters.name: TabBoxCount
parameters.description: Number of CommandManager tab boxes on this CommandManager tab

returns: in-process, unmanaged C++: Pointer to an array of CommandManager tab boxes on this CommandManager tab VBA, VB.NET, C#, and C++/CLI: Not supported See In-process Methods for details about this type of method.
